---
/** Clean report diagram for `_get_cpuia`: what gets found, what gets changed. */
---

<figure
  class="xz-install not-prose"
  role="img"
  aria-label="Simplified hook installer: find sshd, find RSA_public_decrypt GOT slot, overwrite it with the liblzma stub before RELRO."
>
  <p class="xz-install-eyebrow">Hook installer · <code>_get_cpuia</code></p>

  <div class="xz-install-flow">
    <div class="xz-install-step">
      <span>01</span>
      <strong>Find <code>sshd</code></strong>
      <p>Walk the dynamic linker's loaded-object list.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="xz-install-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div>
    <div class="xz-install-step">
      <span>02</span>
      <strong>Find GOT slot</strong>
      <p>Resolve <code>RSA_public_decrypt</code> in <code>sshd</code>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="xz-install-arrow is-hot" aria-hidden="true">→</div>
    <div class="xz-install-step is-hot">
      <span>03</span>
      <strong>Rewrite pointer</strong>
      <p><code>GOT[...]</code> now points to <code>liblzma_stub</code>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="xz-install-note">
    <strong>Why it works:</strong> IFUNC runs before RELRO. The GOT is still writable; once RELRO locks it, the poisoned pointer is frozen in place.
  </div>
</figure>

<style>
  .xz-install {
    margin: 1.5rem auto 1.75rem;
    max-width: 760px;
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--xz-attacker);
    background: var(--page-bg);
  }
  .xz-install-eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--xz-attacker);
  }
  .xz-install code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9em;
    padding: 0.05em 0.25em;
    border-radius: 3px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--page-text) 6%, transparent);
    color: var(--page-text);
  }
  .xz-install-flow {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }
  .xz-install-step {
    padding: 0.8rem 0.85rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--subtle-bg);
  }
  .xz-install-step span {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--xz-defender);
  }
  .xz-install-step strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--page-text);
  }
  .xz-install-step p {
    margin: 0.4rem 0 0;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.42;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .xz-install-step.is-hot {
    border-color: var(--xz-attacker);
    background: var(--xz-attacker-bg);
  }
  .xz-install-step.is-hot span,
  .xz-install-step.is-hot strong { color: var(--xz-attacker); }
  .xz-install-arrow {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .xz-install-arrow.is-hot { color: var(--xz-attacker); }
  .xz-install-note {
    margin-top: 0.85rem;
    padding-top: 0.8rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .xz-install-note strong { color: var(--page-text); }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .xz-install-flow { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .xz-install-arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); min-height: 1rem; }
  }
</style>
